The paper discusses the concept and architecture of an Autonomous Intelligent Cyber defense Agent (AICA) for military systems, which involves cybersecurity (cs.CR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), systems and control (cs.SY), software engineering (cs.SE), and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
